reviewText: Thank you very much for the 3 dvds they are great and really I congratulate  those gymnasts, their coaches and their directors.
It helped me coaching. I like that it helped me through my teaching from level 4 to 7,and sure it will help more for references.
I like this video, I think it is very useful for gymnastics purposes, though I would have like it to present more specific exercises, but the video is good.

Although this DVD is amateur in its production, it's so much better than a book to demonstrate the elements rather than read about them. A DVD with computerized animation would be better, but probably quite expensive.
